{"tid":2372551,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"袁智聰 - 我的 2020 年香港獨立音樂 10+10","createTime":"2021-01-19T18:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T23:49:45.000Z","uid":96034,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a8b7a647afe20dd0e54ad9f44bd4a0f11d72257d","tid":2372551,"uid":96034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"【選擇性失聰】2020年是香港最壞的年代，但我們仍有優秀的本地獨立音樂。為我喜愛的2020年香港音樂做一個記錄，但今年本土獨立音樂的產量並不足以叫我這個「數字控」選出20大專輯，所以我來個10 + 10 &mdash;&mdash;選出我的香港獨立音樂的10大單曲及10大專輯。<br />\n<br />\n1. TAOTAO 《 Ain't No 24/7 Happiness 》<br />\n2. Mousefx 《 See Jah Light 》<br />\n3. 假日貞操 Virgin Vacation 《 5 Step 》<br />\n4. 鍾楚翹CHOR 《 midsommar 》<br />\n5. 南洋派對N.Y.P.D. 《美之 (Mee &amp; Gee)》<br />\n6. R.O.O.T 《非洲的60秒》<br />\n7. Room307 《 My Bonnie 》<br />\n8. 陳嘉 CHANKA 《 Everyday I Die A Little Bit Inside 》<br />\n9. ANWIYCTI 《 Kids 》<br />\n10. DAWN《慌》<br />\n<br />\nSource: HK01<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10首都好正"},{"pid":"533882a7dbd6d4a01be7d059ca9f6345e5c7692e","tid":2372551,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T18:14:17.000Z","msg":"只聽過一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047133e4ad25ace85388b64fd93bbcab8f1b14ca","tid":2372551,"uid":96034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"533882a7dbd6d4a01be7d059ca9f6345e5c7692e","tid":2372551,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T18:14:17.000Z","msg":"只聽過一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T18:22:03.000Z","msg":"未睇呢篇之前都係聽過Root 果首. <br />\n之後上網聽返晒. 喺真係正嘅"},{"pid":"6c995e87d48345ad669445541d8fb9c7a91b72d4","tid":2372551,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T18:38:50.000Z","msg":"支持本地音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00237d233b3c090583148fa6870bd0ed69a223cd","tid":2372551,"uid":41246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0